creator: Quality Health Developers
descriptionHtml:
Have you ever felt unsafe with all the 5G frequencies and waves around you? Are you bothered by feeling EMF? This entertainment blocking app can make you feel more comfortable when going around the streets and having with your friends & family!
Show this app to your friends for even better protection against EMF and 5G network waves!

Features:
⭕ Fancy animations
⭕ Supports Light ☀️ and Dark🌑 mode!
⭕ Long lasting protection

By using the 5G Blocker PLUS there is a high chance that your health increases (not guaranteed). The protector is shown via notification. If you want to pause the health protection there is an option to pause the notification. Afterwards, it's possible to reactivate the 5G protection.

Note:
This app is just for entertainment! Of course, no frequencies are blocked for real as no mobile phone is capable of doing this, am I right? 😉
